  <thing id="raAP83Cart" name="Cartouch of Invulnerability" description="Hakotep&apos;s name has been branded onto the undead dinosaur&apos;s chest. Originally meant as a mark of dominance, the cartouche also protects Sensuret with the effects of a globe of invulnerability. Once per round, a character who attacks the Tribe-Eater (or specifically takes an action to study the undead creature) can attempt a DC 25 Perception check to notice the brand on the creature&apos;s desiccated flesh under its linen wrappings; with a successful DC 35 Knowledge (arcana) check, a character identifies the marking for what it is. The cartouche can be sundered (it has 20 hit points that do not count against the dinosaur&apos;s actual hit point total), at which point the Tribe-Eater loses its invulnerability until it rejuvenates." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Brand grants glove of invulnerability effect." uniqueness="useronce">
